{"tid":1845693,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"娜璉飯係ONCE界入面最垃圾既飯","createTime":"2020-01-27T09:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T01:48:11.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"abba2878668700183a73fe82fe7025c72df05f7b","tid":1845693,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE憑著甜美的外貌<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(?)</strong></span>和出眾的歌唱<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(?)</strong></span>、舞蹈實力<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>(?)</strong></span>，在全球都有許多死忠粉絲，只不過近日成員們深受「私生飯」困擾，彩瑛26日還在Instagram上發文透露自己的的電話號碼遭到流出，不停受到電話、簡訊騷擾，27日這個兇手曝光，竟是之前跟蹤娜璉的一名德國男子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4617/d4617835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4617%2Fd4617835.jpg&h=2ddcdb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE彩瑛電話號碼流出，兇手竟是「娜璉德國跟蹤狂」。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員彩瑛26日透露電話號碼遭到流出後，引起大批粉絲的擔心，只不過網友似乎找出了曝光電話號碼的兇手，就是當時因為跟蹤娜璉而受到Once關注的德國男，網友找到了該男最初的po文，竟然直接把彩瑛的電話號碼公布在推特。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4670/d4670914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4670%2Fd4670914.jpg&h=c8aae800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE彩瑛電話號碼流出，兇手竟是「娜璉德國跟蹤狂」。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n該男不只公布了彩瑛的電話號碼，甚至吆喝其他歌迷幫他一起傳送訊息給彩瑛，問她「為什麼JYP要無視他？為什麼娜璉不能跟他聯絡？」表示自己的所作所為都是為了能更近一步接觸到娜璉，離譜的行徑讓大批粉絲相當髮指。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4670/d4670913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4670%2Fd4670913.jpg&h=c26fe119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲該名「娜璉德國跟蹤狂」發文，令人髮指。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n而在彩瑛發文撻伐私生飯後，該男似乎受到了許多網民的攻擊，不停在推特上傳道歉文，對於把號碼公開一事感到相當抱歉，只不過話鋒一轉他又表示希望彩瑛能夠把貼文刪掉，因為他受到了很多威脅，也讓他感到很傷心，明明自己沒有想要傷害他人的心，為何彩瑛要這樣對他，甚至主張自己公開號碼並沒有錯，錯在於騷擾彩英的那些網民，種種狂傲的言語以及誇張的思想引起大批粉絲的憤怒，紛紛留言要他適可而止。"},{"pid":"fddb95de5d4e922563b548b2edee4bcfc4a3601c","tid":1845693,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5b522a5503adae336562db96235c25bf77bd84","tid":1845693,"uid":208486,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"私生唔係fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41341c3c8ccdc7b8d2bda30c52633c61b601fefd","tid":1845693,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"死癲佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0664425b00438d8033c6ad00f57974b41e7a3215","tid":1845693,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"印狗第2"},{"pid":"7ea05ed98266a516b7f10f8b56d7055b42a7d2ad","tid":1845693,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/YoshTG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYoshTG&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=5ea5682b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YoshTG</a><br />\n條友真係幾癲吓..."},{"pid":"f402ae204083d9f82ac3cad96d7b2ba623baac88","tid":1845693,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7ea05ed98266a516b7f10f8b56d7055b42a7d2ad","tid":1845693,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/YoshTG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYoshTG&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=5ea5682b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YoshTG</a><br />\n條友真係幾癲吓..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ENmATsaU0AI-Q-K?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FENmATsaU0AI-Q-K%3Fformat%3Djpg